data.description: Enjoy functional living in this spacious 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home. Featuring a 2-car garage with a new door, a large fenced lot for privacy, and a generous deck for outdoor enjoyment. Inside, enjoy the warmth of wood floors and the coziness of a fireplace. The open layout connects the living, dining, and modern kitchen areas seamlessly. Retreat to the primary suite with vaulted ceilings and its own bathroom oasis. Located close to shopping, dining, and major highways. Don't miss out—schedule a tour today!
